message.entry: Image message type is not supported. The 'Msg' input must be a ROS message with one of the following types: {0}.
Image encoding {0} requires the alpha channel to be of type {1}.
Image encoding {0} requires the image to be of type {1}.
The Alpha input must have only one channel.
The Image input ({0}) and Alpha input ({1}) do not have compatible sizes.

The 'Write Image' block expects an input length of {0}, but an image of length {1} is provided. Set the maximum length of Data property for 'sensor_msgs/Image' message to {1} using variable size messages.
